#EXTM3U url-tvg="https://aeroplay.tv/aero-review-demo.xml"
# Aero - demo playlist for App Review and for the App Store screenshots.
#
# The guide URL is declared in the header above, so adding this one playlist URL
# also brings in the guide - no second step for the reviewer.
#
# Aero ships with no content and no bundled playlists. This playlist exists only
# so an App Review reviewer can exercise the player without supplying their own
# provider, and so the App Store screenshots can show the app in use without any
# commercial broadcast channel appearing on screen.
#
# Every entry is openly licensed or synthetic:
#   - Live test card  SMPTE colour bars with an on-screen clock, streamed 24/7 by
#                     Unified Streaming's public demo service. Generated, not filmed:
#                     there is no underlying work and nothing to license. It is the
#                     only genuinely live entry, so it is what exercises live playback
#                     and rewind - and the burnt-in clock makes that legible: pause
#                     freezes it, rewind shows an earlier time.
#   - Blender films   (c) Blender Foundation, Creative Commons Attribution 3.0.
#                     Served from Blender's own host (and the Internet Archive).
#   - Apple streams   Apple's public HLS reference/sample streams.
#
# Nothing here is a commercial broadcast channel.
#
# NASA TV was here until 2026-07-15. Both endpoints are DEAD: ntv1/ntv2.akamaized.net
# still return 200 for master.m3u8, but every variant inside 404s and the masters were
# last modified 2024-03-16 - Akamai is serving a two-year-old tombstone. Those URLs are
# still copied across dozens of public playlists, which is exactly why they look alive.
# Lesson for whoever edits this next: check a SEGMENT, not the master. A master is just
# a text file, and a text file can outlive the stream by years.

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="live.testcard" tvg-name="Live Test Card" group-title="Live",Live Test Card
https://demo.unified-streaming.com/k8s/live/stable/live.isml/.m3u8

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="blender.bbb" tvg-name="Big Buck Bunny" group-title="Films",Big Buck Bunny
https://download.blender.org/peach/bigbuckbunny_movies/big_buck_bunny_720p_h264.mov

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="blender.sintel" tvg-name="Sintel" group-title="Films",Sintel
https://archive.org/download/Sintel/sintel-2048-surround.mp4

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="blender.tos" tvg-name="Tears of Steel" group-title="Films",Tears of Steel
https://download.blender.org/demo/movies/ToS/tears_of_steel_720p.mov

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="blender.ed" tvg-name="Elephants Dream" group-title="Films",Elephants Dream
https://archive.org/download/ElephantsDream/ed_hd.mp4

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="apple.hevc" tvg-name="Apple Reference (HEVC)" group-title="Reference",Apple Reference (HEVC)
https://devstreaming-cdn.apple.com/videos/streaming/examples/bipbop_adv_example_hevc/master.m3u8

#EXTINF:-1 tvg-id="apple.fmp4" tvg-name="Apple Reference (fMP4)" group-title="Reference",Apple Reference (fMP4)
https://devstreaming-cdn.apple.com/videos/streaming/examples/img_bipbop_adv_example_fmp4/master.m3u8
